title: Suzuka 8 Hours 2015 Full Race SVID 360p HEVC-[f1d]
description:
The 2015 "Coca-Cola Zero" Suzuka 8 Hours

On July 26, 2015, Suzuka Circuit in Ino, Suzuka City, Mie Prefecture, Japan, hosted the 38th annual 8-hour FIM motorcycle endurance race.

With its iconic 'S' curves, 130R, Degner Curve and Spoon Curve, Suzuka is a favourite among both auto- and motorcycle racers around the world. The 8 Hours has an atmosphere rivalled by few other motorsport events. The 8 Hours, hosted at Suzuka since 1978, is an event steeped in history and lore.

Honda has seen nearly 20 years of domination at this event. Will Ducati step up their game with its Panigale finally seeing results in WorldSBK? Will Yamaha's refresh of their venerable R1 enable them to break a 19-year streak off of the top step?

Watch and see!
